query: SELECT c.name as categoryName, p.partNumber, p.name as productName FROM product_categories pc JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id JOIN products p ON pc.productId = p.id WHERE c.id IN (21, 31, 41, 52, 60003) ORDER BY c.id LIMIT 20;
